"Load your CSV data in some native tool to your platform, select and copy it "
"to the clipboard"
msgstr ""

#: html/cool-help.html%2Bdiv.div.div.div.ol.li:773-7
msgid ""
"Activate the <span class=\"productname\">{productname}</span> spreadsheet "
"window."
